<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I'm currently reading #4 in the series and I have loved all these books. But for the LIFE of me I can't remember the ending of the 1st! Could anyone message me a brief summary of the 1st book Now You See Me? I would be very appreciative! I do remember there was something to do with 2 sisters and 1 of them was the jack-ripper-copycat possibly? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
