<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/919523-jean"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_100x100-6433b08cbe793211f55e184d39e84c4d.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/919523-jean">Jean</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Lacey was really Victoria and her sister Cathy didn't die in the boat. Cathy was doing all the murders. So Cathy went to prison as Victoria and Lacey <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Lacey was really Victoria and her sister Cathy didn't die in the boat. Cathy was doing all the murders. So Cathy went to prison as Victoria and Lacey will continue to be Lacey. Victoria took the identity of Lacey when the real Lacey died of an overdose.<br />At the end, Cathy had invited Lacey to help with the last murder by sending her a knife. Lacey figured out where to find her and broke away from Joesbury so she could rescue the victim. When Cathy gave her the knife to kill the victim, Lacey stabbed herself instead and they were able to get away. Joesbury was shot but survived.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
