<span id="freeTextContainer4584341643416837675"><br/><b>***BR with <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/11644154-la-lionne' rel='nofollow noopener'>Her Highness</a> and <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/3150990-samantha' rel='nofollow noopener'>Samantha</a> on June 18!! :D</b><br/><br/>Darkness...fear...terror...rape...blood...murder...rebirth...revenge...Jack the Ripper.<br/><br/>Speaking of which, how many of you think <b>Jack the Ripper</b> was actually a woman?<br/><br/><b>Jill the Reaper</b><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1383460948i/6568391._SY540_.jpg' alt='Hosted by imgur.com' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>I have to admit it never crossed my mind until I read this book. <br/><br/><blockquote>
