      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/14673027-now-you-see-me">Quotes from Now You See Me</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
